{"tid":1042264,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"股票組合最佳化計數機","createTime":"2019-03-01T12:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-01T15:08:59.000Z","uid":235009,"like":8,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"185ddd636aa0c0ca073f91532e9b2ea29363ba50","tid":1042264,"uid":235009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:22:57.000Z","msg":"今次我整左個係大學讀econ既人要學既efficient frontier<br />\nEfficient frontier係用黎知一個投資組合最好既weighting係咩<br />\n例如我想買823同700<br />\n係唔係50% 50%咁買好?<br />\n定係其中一隻買多啲好?<br />\n<br />\n要搵個optimal weighting好易 (假設目標係要最大化sharpe ratio)<br />\n只係將唔同既weighting組合計個expected return同standard deviation<br />\n然後搵邊一個組合有最大既expected return/standard deviation就搞點<br />\n用823同700做例子就會有呢個graph<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AzOyRxX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAzOyRxX.png&h=c3ff2bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最大既expected return/standard deviation其實就係最大既slope<br />\n所以肉眼都睇得出最大應該係highlight個位到<br />\n呢個位係 700:34%; 823: 65%<br />\n所以根據efficient frontier<br />\n買700同823就應該擺35%係700; 65%係823<br />\n<br />\n但係計還計<br />\n實際上最好既weighting基本上係無可能知<br />\n例如2010-01-01到2012-12-31既最好weighting係700: 7%; 823: 92%<br />\n2012-01-01到2014-12-31就係700: 44%; 823: 55%<br />\n講到尾都係會有overfitting既問題<br />\n所以用戈陣都要自己諗下點用<br />\n<br />\n我整個圖其實有一個好大既缺點 <br />\n就係show唔到啲一點點係咩weighting<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以基本上張圖係廢<br />\n如果有人識chart js又知點show到既話唔該同我講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後提下<br />\n我個計法係random計1000個weighting組合<br />\n所以如果你input得越多股票<br />\n就越會包唔晒所有組合<br />\n你可以做既係submit多幾次計多幾個組合<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkportfolioanalysis.com/analysis/efficient_frontier/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkportfolioanalysis.com%2Fanalysis%2Fefficient_frontier%2F&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CwHlXPv3B7QU%2BsV1%2BUkEKpk%3D&h=60451e33\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkportfolioanalysis.com/analysis/efficient_frontier/</a>"},{"pid":"ce6e7e8716b65822f70660a7def993ee00f4d884","tid":1042264,"uid":76105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"我屌you 個 mother 啦 ！"},{"pid":"a30347f13e205caaa17d5fc3c4354e5aeee034a2","tid":1042264,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"點解會99-0?"},{"pid":"a7ff58ff95b09385198bad8e5e0d85ba9c9a8a4f","tid":1042264,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:04:55.000Z","msg":"你估你股神咩<br />\n搞咁撚多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b99f73e8ab6f1335d795e677ff4b992d6f0188","tid":1042264,"uid":49574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T13:06:26.000Z","msg":"書入面就有用"},{"pid":"fa087b1fdccf453bb76e20ed0305ccfe797e2861","tid":1042264,"uid":235009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a30347f13e205caaa17d5fc3c4354e5aeee034a2","tid":1042264,"uid":18948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:41:35.000Z","msg":"點解會99-0?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:15:54.000Z","msg":"我廢事麻煩所以無理round off問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add6194ef75baf459e0ec0a9013ac8f37c4bad5c","tid":1042264,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:18:06.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"149a5ce5f26594642160469f52c84fa5a5ee0ebd","tid":1042264,"uid":67049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:26:05.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"5570d3ff193b769bea3c0a827fe4b0b3870add07","tid":1042264,"uid":234307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6e7e8716b65822f70660a7def993ee00f4d884","tid":1042264,"uid":76105,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T12:33:06.000Z","msg":"我屌you 個 mother 啦 ！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T14:27:34.000Z","msg":"屌 笑到我收唔撚到聲"},{"pid":"3996414ed7aa3924f1e0be6d5026ae0fb77a43c6","tid":1042